# Assets Audio Directory

This directory will contain all game audio including:
- music_main_theme.mp3
- sfx_card_play.wav
- sfx_clash_win.wav, sfx_clash_lose.wav, sfx_clash_tie.wav
- sfx_damage_take.wav
- sfx_armor_gain.wav
- sfx_sword_ability.wav, sfx_shield_ability.wav, sfx_spear_ability.wav
- sfx_ui_click.wav
